snippet: Jennifer O’Neill scored a career-high 43 points, including the go-ahead basket in the fourth overtime, and No. 5 Kentucky beat No. 9 Baylor, 133-130, in Arlington, Texas.
abstract: Kentucky beats Baylor, 133-130, in women's college basketball, marking highest-scoring Division 1 women's game in history.
